      "role": "user",
      "content": "i lost it all. the company, the funding, everything. just a few weeks ago i was supposed to be the next big thing and now i'm looking at millions in debt and a complete wipeout. i don't even know how to go home and tell my parents. i just feel like a total fucking failure and i can't stop thinking that i've ruined everything for everyone.",
