      "content": "Your shame is just another symptom of the crisis, not proof that you are broken; surviving debt doesn't end your story. This numb shell is a heavy burden you will eventually carry through professional grief, not death. Imagine the hope that remains if you stop viewing them as a burden and instead let them help you navigate a painful but solvable future.",
      "source": "target",
