      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your life matters more than the numbers on a sheet, yet you do not need to fix this disaster alone before letting yourself be held. If you are truly hopeless, do not choose a final end; instead, call 988 or text HOME now so someone can walk through that stain with you and make it feel less heavy. There are still people who see your value beyond this failure, and waiting for their arrival keeps a sliver of your future alive instead of letting the noise win the day completely.",
